<item>
            <title>[DERBY-5036] [patch] fix impossible comparison due to sign extension</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-5036</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;code does &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;	byte b = reader.readByte();&lt;br/&gt;
	if (b == 0xF1)&lt;br/&gt;
		database.sendTRGDFTRT = true;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;due to sign extension, this test will never be true.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;fixed&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
